sequenceDiagram
    title Secuencia: Registro y Aprobación de Factura (UC-CXP-001, UC-CXP-002)

    actor Analista as Analista Financiero
    actor Gerente as Gerente Financiero
    participant ExpAPI as accounts-payable-exp-api
    participant InvAPI as invoice-management-api
    participant ERPAPI as erp-integration-api
    participant LfcAPI as invoice-lifecycle-api
    participant ERP as ERP System

    Note over Analista,ERP: UC-CXP-001: Registro de Factura

    Analista->>ExpAPI: POST /invoices {supplier_id, invoice_number, amount...}
    ExpAPI->>InvAPI: POST /invoices
    InvAPI->>ERPAPI: GET /erp/suppliers/{supplierId}/validate
    ERPAPI->>ERP: GET /suppliers/{supplierId}
    ERP-->>ERPAPI: {status: ACTIVE}
    ERPAPI-->>InvAPI: {valid: true}
    InvAPI->>InvAPI: Verificar unicidad (supplier_id + invoice_number)
    InvAPI->>LfcAPI: POST /invoice-lifecycle/{id}/transition {to_status: PENDING}
    LfcAPI-->>InvAPI: {current_status: PENDING}
    InvAPI-->>ExpAPI: 201 {id, status: PENDING}
    ExpAPI-->>Analista: 201 Factura creada (PENDING)

    Note over Analista,ERP: UC-CXP-002: Aprobación de Factura

    Gerente->>ExpAPI: POST /invoices/{id}/approve {comment}
    ExpAPI->>InvAPI: POST /invoices/{id}/approve
    InvAPI->>LfcAPI: GET /invoice-lifecycle/{id}/current-state
    LfcAPI-->>InvAPI: {current_status: PENDING}
    InvAPI->>LfcAPI: POST /invoice-lifecycle/{id}/transition {to_status: APPROVED, performed_by: gerente_id}
    LfcAPI-->>InvAPI: {current_status: APPROVED}
    InvAPI-->>ExpAPI: 200 {status: APPROVED}
    ExpAPI-->>Gerente: 200 Factura aprobada
